locality: Forestiere Prov. Nimba Mountains, SMFG iron mining concession. Forested slopes beyond Base Geologique. Collected with Jean-Yves Serein.
Mindu Hill SSW of Morogoro town: mist effected Uapaca kirkii woodland on the S-end of the main ridge very rich in epiphytic and terricolous bryophytes.
Mount Nimba Strict Nature Reserve. Along road cut to old mine site. <30682-30720>
Dedza District. 15 km from Ntcheu/Dedza junction with Lake Shore Road. Chincherere Hills. Small isolated hills surrounded by low forest. <10797-10839>
Loma Mountains, west foot of Bintumani, alt. 5000 ft.

Betroka, Kalambatritra. Forêt d'Analamaro. Forêt 25 m de haut, emergents généralement composés de Sloanea rhodantha, Ocotea sp.. Strate supérieure ayant une hauteur comprise entre 15 à 25 m, composées de Ravenea sp., lianes (Fabaceae; Strongylodon sp.). Strate moyenne de 4 à 10 m, constituée par des jeunes arbres: Dombeya sp. Grewia, Oncostemon, Chrysophyllum sp.. Strate inférieure: Oncostemon, Rubiaceae, Acanthaceae, Urticaceae.
Stapleford Forest, Rupere, near Research Station, 1832 D2.

Cathkin Peak Forest Reserve, ca. 53 km E of Estcourt. First gorge below falls of Sterkspruit River (grid 29.29 AB)
